==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tipper
<hw>Tip"per</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A kind of ale brewed
with brackish water obtained from a particular well; -- so called from
the first brewer of it, one Thomas <xex>Tipper</xex>.</def>
<mark>[Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

